job_overview: Join InnoSoft Solutions as a Data Analyst and contribute to data-driven decision-making.
job_desc: Join our team as a Data Analyst and play a key role in analyzing and interpreting data to inform business decisions. Proficiency in Python and SQL is required, along with experience in data visualization tools. Responsibilities include collecting, cleaning, and analyzing data to provide insights to stakeholders. Strong analytical skills and attention to detail are essential for success in this role.
